					item: "gtceu:lv_gas_turbine"
					type: "item"
				}
				{
					id: "PS02000000000026"
					item: "gtceu:mv_gas_turbine"
					type: "item"
				}
				{
					id: "PS02000000000027"
					item: "gtceu:hv_gas_turbine"
					type: "item"
				}
			]
			title: "Gas Turbines"
			x: 5.0d
			y: -6.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["PS01000000000017"]
			description: ["GTCEu Combustion Engines burn liquid fuels: Bio-Diesel, Diesel, Cetane-Boosted Diesel, Gasoline, and High-Octane Gasoline in ascending output order. Bio-Diesel is the earliest accessible fuel — produced from plant oils (Pam's Harvestcraft sunflower or Mystical Agriculture oil seeds) in the Chemical Reactor. Standard Diesel requires the Oil Refinery chain. The LV Combustion Engine on Bio-Diesel provides a significant EU/t bump over steam sources. Scale to MV and HV Combustion Engines as the refinery chain matures; High-Octane Gasoline in HV Combustion Engines is the primary single-block EU source before multiblock machines are viable."]
			id: "PS01000000000018"
			rewards: [{
