			y: -7.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["PS01000000000018"]
			description: ["The Large Steam Turbine is a 3×3×4 multiblock structure that multiplies steam-to-EU conversion efficiency substantially over single-block turbines. It requires Turbine Blades made from Steel or higher alloys; blade material determines efficiency tier. The structure consumes more steam but produces EU at a far higher rate per unit of steam than individual turbines. The Large Combustion Engine and Large Gas Turbine follow the same multiblock pattern but burn liquid fuels and gas respectively. Build at least one Large multiblock generator before HV-tier GTCEu machines become the primary power drain — they are the step that makes an EU surplus feel achievable."]
			id: "PS01000000000019"
			rewards: [{
