		{
			dependencies: ["PS01000000000023"]
			description: ["Flux Networks replaces all RF cable infrastructure with a wireless distribution system. Flux Dust is the crafting base — smelt it from materials at the Flux Anvil or via the recipe in JEI. The Flux Controller manages the network; each network requires exactly one. The Flux Plug draws RF from any RF-producing block, cable, or battery adjacent to it. The Flux Point injects RF into any RF-consuming block anywhere in the world, regardless of distance. There is no cable length limit and no transmission loss. Build Flux Networks as soon as you have HV-tier materials and Flux Dust production — it eliminates the cable complexity of large multi-building power setups permanently."]
			id: "PS01000000000024"
